                  clearing houses and trading venues
                </span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <span class="text-gray-dark">
                  Is integrated into global markets having signed framework agreements and has established open
                  lines with multiple professional clients and eligible counterparties.
                </span>
              </li>
            </ul>
